SetVoiceDspLoop.Help:
USAGE:
    set voicedsploop enable{0:disable,1:enable} type{0:TDM,1:IP} port{1,2}
OPTIONS:
    enable  : {0:disable,1:enable}
    type    : {0:TDM,1:IP}
    port    : {1,2}

SetVoicePortLoop.Help:
USAGE:
    set voiceportloop enable{0:disable,1:enable} type{0:TDM,1:IP} port{1,2}
OPTIONS:
    enable  : {0:disable,1:enable}
    type    : {0:TDM,1:IP}
    port    : {1,2}

SetVoiceDebug.Help:
USAGE:
    set voicedebug switch{on, off}
OPTIONS:
    switch  : {on:enable,off:disable}

SetVoiceSignalingPrint.Help:
USAGE:
    set VoiceSignalingPrint switch{on, off}
OPTIONS:
    switch  : {on:enable,off:disable}

SetVoiceLineTest.Help:
USAGE:
    set voicelinetest portnum{[1,2]}
OPTIONS:
    portnum : value range{[1,2]}

SetEthPortMirror.Help:
USAGE:
    set ethportmirror sourceport {value} destport {value} mirrordate {0:out/1:in/2:all} enable {0/1}
OPTIONS:
    sourceport  : value range [1-4:eth/5:cpu/6:pon] 
    destport    : value range [1-4] 
    mirrordate  : {0:out/1:in/2:all}
    enable      : {0/1}

LswStatShow.Help:
usage:
amp show stat {rx/tx/drop/queue-{queue-id}}
amp show bc {vlanid}
amp show hybrid {vlanid}
